{"tid":2410650,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"空調vs冷氣","createTime":"2021-02-16T20:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T20:59:37.000Z","uid":251736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2f07d8be915308faf607e37845d18be641046baf","tid":2410650,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:06:19.000Z","msg":"咁大家入得黎，係人都知冷氣係啱，空調唔啱但有野想連登巴絲打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟作文要用冷氣呢個詞語，但係實比prof話係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，想大家幫幫手諗理據<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到嘅理據<br />\n點解喺自己民族嘅地方用自己民族嘅語言係錯<br />\n<br />\n點解喺自己民族嘅地方要就其他民族嘅語言<br />\n<br />\n如果喺自己民族嘅地方都唔可以用自己嘅語言，咁仲有邊度可以用，香港話或者廣東話係咪會死<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到反方理據<br />\n<br />\n寫文最緊要傳達自己嘅意思，對方睇唔睇得明最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你寫文都會寫xx的xx而唔係xx嘅xx, 所以根本就冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n書面語係空調，口語先係冷氣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果prof講出侮辱香港話嘅言論，我實屌柒個prof。到時我會請比出好理據嘅巴絲打食黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4657300f8a963cf85ac6bb5eb62d980270e6c3ef","tid":2410650,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:08:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d50ec28cfc8ae5eb8f6e5ffe25465710e7f55a4e","tid":2410650,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:09:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20e10e819555c12e738f845d2a765c86d15f7715","tid":2410650,"uid":189160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:09:23.000Z","msg":"但冷氣機會出暖氣<br />\n<br />\n咁係冷氣機定暖氣機？"},{"pid":"76932901d229f0e3150cc41b792849c9166155c1","tid":2410650,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:09:29.000Z","msg":"讀乜作文要用中文? 香港專上教育唔係100%英語教學架咩"},{"pid":"652e862347e946f41f36efa44c349c7a2b8df31c","tid":2410650,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76932901d229f0e3150cc41b792849c9166155c1","tid":2410650,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:09:29.000Z","msg":"讀乜作文要用中文? 香港專上教育唔係100%英語教學架咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:10:30.000Z","msg":"讀中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b06bd1320ee425b728bdac40ade11185c8fcc7","tid":2410650,"uid":27716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76932901d229f0e3150cc41b792849c9166155c1","tid":2410650,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:09:29.000Z","msg":"讀乜作文要用中文? 香港專上教育唔係100%英語教學架咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:10:38.000Z","msg":"間間都有科中文必修架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74871fd80eef144eedacfa221c9dff52b5356827","tid":2410650,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:11:14.000Z","msg":"幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355d6dd182eaea5161ec28e2dcc8645614b9519c","tid":2410650,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd5e4448ce90e3dab9e82c30e68ca6cde9a23c3","tid":2410650,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:12:59.000Z","msg":"大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6164131d2652171d3313d6418301267d0211033","tid":2410650,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:14:49.000Z","msg":"help<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e565c22590092afa28fca6b53c0022e3975050","tid":2410650,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:21:14.000Z","msg":"香港話只係方言，邊上到大台<br />\n此po議員"},{"pid":"51eeba4894bef77e7b892f5c855a7b69a80b1e72","tid":2410650,"uid":39706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:21:58.000Z","msg":"根本香港一直以嚟都係叫冷氣, 係大陸先叫空調, 等於日本叫便當, 而我哋叫飯盒唔係錯喎.  樓主睇吓日立個官網都叫冷氣機, 唔通你個 Prof 又話日立錯?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hitachi-hk.com.hk/tc/products/air-conditioner.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hitachi-hk.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fproducts%2Fair-conditioner.html&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=84dca1ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hitachi-hk.com.hk/tc/products/air-conditioner.html</a>"},{"pid":"3977a51a1453f2f7a4273f2b2b980eec14c978a4","tid":2410650,"uid":260184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:23:47.000Z","msg":"由細到大讀書同書寫作文都係用冷氣機，就算報紙課本都係寫冷氣機，咩叫空調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2f4640cfc490a0cef2667e6aec47d50b76a45b","tid":2410650,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:24:08.000Z","msg":"空調的主要作用是控制室內空氣的流動，並調節空氣溫度、濕度和淨化空氣，使大廈內的人能有一個舒適的環境和良好的室內空氣質素。<br />\n<br />\n一般來說，空調系統可以分為房間冷氣機和中央系統兩大類。<br />\n<br />\n房間冷氣機（例如窗口式和分體式冷氣機）是住宅類樓宇最常用的空調系統。整個製冷循環都在冷氣機中完成。下圖為窗口式冷氣機的內部結構。<br />\n  <br />\n香港講開冷氣多"},{"pid":"ebf37872dd480d45c10e48e7a78857cf45e5f8c6","tid":2410650,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51eeba4894bef77e7b892f5c855a7b69a80b1e72","tid":2410650,"uid":39706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:21:58.000Z","msg":"根本香港一直以嚟都係叫冷氣, 係大陸先叫空調, 等於日本叫便當, 而我哋叫飯盒唔係錯喎.  樓主睇吓日立個官網都叫冷氣機, 唔通你個 Prof 又話日立錯?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hitachi-hk.com.hk/tc/products/air-conditioner.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hitachi-hk.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fproducts%2Fair-conditioner.html&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=84dca1ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hitachi-hk.com.hk/tc/products/air-conditioner.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:42:39.000Z","msg":"thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bb17bbf94b3e91327eb9097333f342b029a67f","tid":2410650,"uid":251736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3977a51a1453f2f7a4273f2b2b980eec14c978a4","tid":2410650,"uid":260184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:23:47.000Z","msg":"由細到大讀書同書寫作文都係用冷氣機，就算報紙課本都係寫冷氣機，咩叫空調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:43:12.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ece86c7145b10b40d71f5e9fe82679e31569728","tid":2410650,"uid":105031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:56:20.000Z","msg":"香港大部份都係冷氣機，因為香港係亞熱帶，唔需要暖氣...所以只會係冷氣機。<br />\n大陸有地方會好撚凍，所以係有冷暖功能，所以叫空氣調節"},{"pid":"a8b6505f00792247859649978793f1e19ad6432f","tid":2410650,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T20:59:37.000Z","msg":"香港地唔會有人叫冷氣做空調，一係叫冷暖氣機<br />\n<br />\n會叫空調嘅應該係台灣或者中国之類嘅地區<br />\n<br />\n不過書面語唔等於蝗語，你會寫的士定出租車，巴士定公交車？書面語唔係用蝗語嘅藉口，用書面語都要用返當地常用嘅叫法，所以一定係寫冷氣"}]}